{
  "stem": "449.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he said that that commander of the camp was really a thief.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was an-- he was an Algerian-- he was an Algerian officer.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And just two days he went on vacation.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Always he was there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Only for two days there was a Jewish commander there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You see?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And God told me, you go there with the packet.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Just on this day, you go there, when the other son of a bitch is not there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You will find it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "What a luck, you see.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Here you have the train, God's finger.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Here you have this accident that I just go on the-- on a day when the-- when there is a human being there who has pity with me and gives me back the family.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "All right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now the-- now I-- I have paper.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I have the family.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But what shall I do with the kids?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I give them to the Quakers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my wife and I, we have a good time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A good time, you can imagine a good time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because there was-- there was-- the [NON-ENGLISH] was gone.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] was gone.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was only the-- the Quakers but the Quakers were out, far away from us in the-- in the camp.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we had-- didn't have-- But in the meantime comes the-- comes the visa.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The visa we have.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And which I-- from the camp, you know, from the prison camp, I was allowed, under guard-- I had always a guard, a military guard with me-- to visit the consulate for-- for the visa.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we got-- we got the visa.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now we-- we are going to go to Bordeaux, and take a boat and go to the America.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we want to go to Bordeaux.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Bordeaux is closed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No boats anymore.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
